latestIgtvVideos.caption:
.

.Hey people!
So this is my first igtv . And also something that I’ve tried for the first time . I was very excited to do this and at the same time very very nervous and dicey about posting it but then I read this quote ‘ there will always be someone who will be unhappy with you no matter what you do, so fuck it’ and I thought to myself umm okay I should give it a try. I have always loved fashion and everything related to it and have always enjoyed engaging with any kind of work related to it . So here it is.. 
also a big bigggg shoutout to my homies @soundaryashrivastava @sanjittttt_ @dimplesolankii @whyareyouevenhere_ for always pushing me and supporting me in everything that I do❤️ love you guys
.

.

.

.

Do let me know what you feel about it and if it helped you in any way.. I’d really love that
So yaa 😌❤️
